An operation entails moving the mouse to a different region on the screen, clicking the mouse, or pressing a key shortcut. For clarity repeated actions of uncertain length (such as numerous clicks to form a polygon or navigating the open file dialogue) are counted as one in the evaluation.

Open an image
1: Start program -> navigate open file dialogue
   2
2: Start program -> click 'Open image' -> navigate open file dialogue
   Start program -> press Ctrl + o -> navigate open file dialogue
   3

Mark an object
1: Click polygon points -> move to controls -> click 'Finish current label'
   Click polygon points -> press Alt + n
   max 3 min 2
2: Click polygon points (final point completes)
   1

Add the label
1: Type label text -> move to label box -> click 'OK'
   Type label text -> press Enter key
   max 3 min 2
2: Type label text -> move to label box -> click 'OK'
   Type label text -> press Enter key
   max 3 min 2
   
Edit the label
1: Move to controls -> click 'Toggle mode' -> move to image -> click polygon -> move to controls -> click 'Rename' -> type label text -> move to label box -> click 'OK'
   Press Alt + t -> click polygon -> press Alt + r -> type label text -> press Enter key
   max 9 min 5
2: Move to label list -> click label -> move to controls -> click 'Edit Label' -> type label text -> move to label box -> click 'OK'
   Right-click polygon -> type label text -> press Enter key
   max 7 min 3

Mark another object
1: Move to controls -> click 'Toggle mode' -> move to image -> click polygon points -> move to controls -> click 'Finish current label' -> type label text -> move to label box -> click 'OK'
   Press Alt + t -> click polygon points -> press Alt + n -> type label text -> press Enter key
   max 9 min 5
2: Move to image -> click polygon points -> type label text -> move to label box -> click 'OK'
   Move to image -> click polygon points -> type label text -> press Enter key
   max 5 min 4

Save
1: Move to controls -> click 'Save image tags' -> navigate save file dialogue
   Press Alt + s -> navigate save file dialogue
   max 3 min 2
2: Move to controls -> click 'Save' -> move to message dialogue -> click 'OK' to dismiss -> navigate save file dialogue
   Press Ctrl + s -> press Enter to dismiss message dialogue -> navigate save file dialogue
   max 5 min 3

Open another image
1: Move to controls -> click 'Open' -> navigate open file dialogue
   Press Alt + o -> navigate open file dialogue
   max 3 min 2
2: Click 'Open image' -> navigate open file dialogue
   Press Ctrl + o -> navigate open file dialogue
   2

Mark a lamppost
1: Click polygon points -> move to controls -> click 'Finish current label' -> type label text -> move to label box -> click 'OK'
   click polygon points -> press Alt + n -> type label text -> press Enter key
   max 6 min 4
2: Move to image -> click polygon points -> type label text -> move to label box -> click 'OK'
   Move to image -> click polygon points -> type label text -> press Enter key
   max 5 min 4

Move these markings to a different lamppost
1: Move to controls -> click 'Toggle mode' -> move to image -> click polygon -> move to controls -> click 'Start editing' -> move to image -> drag points -> move to controls -> click 'Stop editing'
   Press Alt + t -> click polygon -> press Alt + e -> drag points -> press Alt + e
   max 10 min 5
2: Move to label list -> click label -> move to controls -> click 'Delete Shape' -> move to image -> click polygon points -> type label text -> move to label box -> click 'OK'
   Press Right-Arrow key -> press Up-Arrow or Down-Arrow to select -> press Del key -> click polygon points -> type label text -> press Enter key
   max 9 min 5

Open up the original image
1: Move to controls -> click 'Open' -> navigate open file dialogue
   Press Alt + o -> navigate open file dialogue
   max 3 min 2
2: Click 'Open image' -> move to message dialogue -> click 'OK' to dismiss -> navigate open file dialogue
   Press Ctrl + o -> press Enter to dismiss message dialogue -> navigate open file dialogue
   max 4 min 3

Load the data
1: Move to controls -> click 'Load image tags' -> move to message dialogue -> click 'OK' to dismiss -> navigate open file dialogue
   Press Alt + l -> press Enter to dismiss message dialogue -> navigate open file dialogue
   maz 5 min 3
2: Move to controls -> click 'Load' -> move to message dialogue -> click 'OK' to dismiss
   Press Ctrl + l -> press Enter to dismiss message dialogue
   max 4 min 2

Delete an object
1: move to image -> click polygon -> move to controls -> click 'Delete'
   move to image -> click polygon -> press Alt + d
   max 4 min 3
2: Move to label list -> click label -> move to controls -> click 'Delete Shape'
   Press Right-Arrow key -> press Up-Arrow or Down-Arrow to select -> press Del key
   max 4 min 3

Close the program
1: move to top of window -> click x button
   2
2: move to top of window -> click x button -> move to prompt dialogue -> click 'No' to dismiss
   move to top of window -> click x button -> press Alt + n to dismiss prompt dialogue
   max 4 min 3